|I_{n+p}-I_{n}| =  \left\lvert\int_{n\delta}^{(n+p)\delta} \frac{\sin\ t}{t}  dt \right\lvert  \leq \int_{n\delta}^{(n+p)\delta} \frac{\left\lvert\sin t\ \right\lvert}{t}  dt = \frac{1} {n\delta}\int_{n\delta}^{M} \left\lvert\sin t\right\lvert dt \ \leq \frac{2} {n\delta} \lneq \epsilon
M \in [n\delta, (n+p)\delta]
